SNVs and indels may be encoded as 64-bit integers called RSVR IDs. To compute an RSVR ID for a given variant, the following expression is evaluated:\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
